---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
    <Header />

    <main class="pt-24 min-h-screen">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold font-display text-white mb-8">
                Privacy Policy
            </h1>
            <div class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">Last updated: January 2024</p>

                <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 space-y-6">
                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                            1. Information We Collect
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                            We collect information you provide directly: email
                            address, name, payment information for
                            subscriptions. We also collect usage data including
                            prompts submitted, websites generated, and
                            interaction with our service.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                            2. How We Use Your Information
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                            We use your information to provide and improve our
                            service, process payments, send service updates, and
                            provide customer support. We do not sell your
                            personal information to third parties.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                            3. Data Storage and Security
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                            Your data is stored securely using industry-standard
                            encryption. We implement appropriate technical and
                            organizational measures to protect your personal
                            information against unauthorized access.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                            4. AI and Generated Content
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                            Prompts you submit may be processed by AI systems
                            for generation purposes. Generated code is yours to
                            own and use. We may use anonymized data to improve
                            our AI models.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                            5. Cookies and Tracking
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                            We use essential cookies for authentication and
                            session management. Analytics cookies help us
                            understand usage patterns. You can control cookie
                            preferences in your browser settings.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                            6. Third-Party Services
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                            We use third-party services for payment processing
                            (secure payment providers), analytics, and AI
                            processing. These services have their own privacy
                            policies.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                            7. Your Rights
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                            You have the right to access, correct, or delete
                            your personal data. You can request a copy of your
                            data or account deletion by contacting support. EU
                            users have additional rights under GDPR.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                            8. Data Retention
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                            We retain your account data while your account is
                            active. You can request deletion at any time. Some
                            data may be retained for legal compliance purposes.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                            9. Contact Us
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                            For privacy-related questions or requests, contact
                            us at privacy@genapps.online
                        </p>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</Layout>
